 new and existing customers. Voting on BBNaija season 5 will also be available via website, SMS and Mobi site. Vanguard By Ayo Onikoyi With the countdown to the season five premiere of Africa’s popular reality TV show, Big Brother Naija officially on, MultiChoice Nigeria has revealed that this season’s winner will walk away with a whopping N85m grand prize. The grand prize which includes a N30m cash prize makes this… July 14, 2020 In "Entertainment" Another season of Big Brother Naija is here with its highly anticipated premiere which kicked off last Sunday. This season show packed full with much excitement and cash reward worth N60 million higher than the previous seasons carries quality said a management source of the MultiChoice. July 8, 2019 In "News" As the countdown to the eagerly anticipated fourth season of Big Brother Naija heats up, MultiChoice Nigeria has announced that it will treat fans of the popular reality TV show to an exclusive reunion show and special pop-up channel on DStv and GOtv starting in March. March 2, 2019 In "Entertainment"